"Why I Hate The Movie Shrek"
Subscribe to my mailing list at Raananhershberg.com #standupcomedy #jokes #haha #shrek

2023 was an incredible year. I got to be in a devil’s threesome with me, my girlfriend, and the Devil. I went to a Chappelle show and was privileged to see one of the greatest black comedic voices of our time Matt Rife open for him. We found out my girlfriend has O.C.D. after she freaked out when I tracked dog shit into the apartment for the 3rd time in a month (it’s extremely hard to live with someone who has that disorder but I’m trying to make it work). Elon Musk posted ‘it’s insanity that transgender people want to be referred to by another name’ on Twitter, a platform he then asked for everyone to refer to by a different name. Robert Kennedy proved to the world that he possesses the same amazing qualities as his Uncle John: leadership, no brains in his skull, courage. I saw Killers of the Flower Moon when it came out in October and my favorite part by far is when I left the theater fifteen minutes ago. 
Here’s to 2024. Let’s see you top this!
